Interface IQueryList<T extends IDbDto>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of database-layer IDbDto to query

    public interface IQueryList<T extends IDbDto>

      • setExpiration

        void setExpiration(int expiration)
        Set the expiration of objects queried by the query method. This setter allows you to change the expiration from the default value set by the factory.
        Parameters:
        expiration - the time in milliseconds until the object expires in the cache
